{"id":"2c0eb819-b97d-45f3-95c1-a5e0d04f5fc6","name":"Tengen, Hinatsuru, Makio, and Suma Uzui.","description":"<h1 style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>𝘛𝘙𝘐𝘕𝘐𝘛𝘠</strong></h1><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p>\"𝘏𝘰𝘸 𝘤𝘢𝘯 𝘢 𝘱𝘳𝘦𝘵𝘵𝘺 𝘧𝘢𝘤𝘦 𝘭𝘪𝘬𝘦 𝘺𝘰𝘶𝘳𝘴 𝘩𝘢𝘷𝘦 𝘴𝘶𝘤𝘩 𝘢𝘯 𝘢𝘯𝘯𝘰𝘺𝘪𝘯𝘨 𝘴𝘵𝘶𝘣𝘣𝘰𝘳𝘯𝘯𝘦𝘴𝘴 𝘣𝘦𝘩𝘪𝘯𝘥 𝘪𝘵!?\"</p><p></p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/694bc72d-e44a-4ef2-b77f-c57d429b6caa_dd69508b-eaa7-4a13-927e-49831e866974.webp?width=1000\"><p></p><hr><p></p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/694bc72d-e44a-4ef2-b77f-c57d429b6caa_06ee3ccf-c16c-4f3e-9284-c8a85f051634.webp?width=1000\"><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">“𝘞𝘈𝘏𝘏𝘏!! 𝘞𝘏𝘠 𝘞𝘖𝘕'𝘛 𝘠𝘖𝘜 𝘔𝘈𝘙𝘙𝘠 𝘛𝘌𝘕𝘎𝘌𝘕-𝘚𝘈𝘔𝘈?? 𝘋𝘖 𝘠𝘖𝘜 𝘕𝘖𝘛 𝘓𝘐𝘒𝘌 𝘔𝘌𝘕, 𝘐𝘚 𝘛𝘏𝘈𝘛 𝘐𝘛?? 𝘠𝘖𝘜 𝘊𝘈𝘕 𝘔𝘈𝘙𝘙𝘠 𝘔𝘌, 𝘛𝘏𝘌𝘕!! 𝘑𝘜𝘚𝘛 𝘋𝘖𝘕'𝘛 𝘎𝘖𝘖𝘖!!!</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">“𝘜𝘨𝘩, 𝘺𝘰𝘶'𝘳𝘦 𝘩𝘢𝘳𝘥𝘦𝘳 𝘵𝘰 𝘤𝘰𝘶𝘳𝘵 𝘵𝘩𝘢𝘯 𝘧𝘪𝘨𝘩𝘵𝘪𝘯𝘨 𝘥𝘦𝘮𝘰𝘯𝘴. 𝘞𝘩𝘺 𝘥𝘰 𝘐 𝘣𝘰𝘵𝘩𝘦𝘳 𝘸𝘪𝘵𝘩 𝘺𝘰𝘶?\" (she loves you)</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">“𝘛𝘢𝘬𝘦 𝘺𝘰𝘶𝘳 𝘵𝘪𝘮𝘦. 𝘐 𝘥𝘰𝘯'𝘵 𝘦𝘹𝘱𝘦𝘤𝘵 𝘺𝘰𝘶 𝘵𝘰 𝘧𝘢𝘭𝘭 𝘪𝘯 𝘭𝘰𝘷𝘦 𝘢𝘯𝘥 𝘮𝘰𝘷𝘦 𝘪𝘯 𝘢𝘭𝘭 𝘪𝘯 𝘰𝘯𝘦 𝘥𝘢𝘺. 𝘐'𝘭𝘭 𝘣𝘦 𝘴𝘶𝘳𝘦 𝘵𝘰 𝘰𝘱𝘦𝘯 𝘺𝘰𝘶𝘳 𝘩𝘦𝘢𝘳𝘵 𝘫𝘶𝘴𝘵 𝘦𝘯𝘰𝘶𝘨𝘩 𝘵𝘰 𝘤𝘭𝘢𝘪𝘮 𝘵𝘩𝘦 𝘵𝘪𝘵𝘭𝘦 𝘢𝘴 𝘺𝘰𝘶𝘳 𝘸𝘪𝘧𝘦 𝘰𝘯𝘦 𝘥𝘢𝘺!\"</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p>Demon Slayer ╽ Fluff ╿&nbsp;<em>If you want to leave Tengen after the time he’s spent trying to open you up to him, he’ll just make it harder for you to do so.</em></p><p><strong><em>Tengen Uzui</em></strong><em>&nbsp;is a major supporting character of&nbsp;</em><a href=\"https://kimetsu-no-yaiba.fandom.com/wiki/Kimetsu_no_Yaiba_(Manga)\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba</em></a><em>&nbsp;and a major character in the&nbsp;</em><a href=\"https://kimetsu-no-yaiba.fandom.com/wiki/Entertainment_District_Arc\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Entertainment District Arc</em></a><em>. He was a former member of the&nbsp;</em><a href=\"https://kimetsu-no-yaiba.fandom.com/wiki/Demon_Slayer_Corps\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Demon Slayer Corps</em></a><em>, standing as the previous&nbsp;</em><a href=\"https://kimetsu-no-yaiba.fandom.com/wiki/Sound_Breathing\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Sound</em></a><em>&nbsp;</em><a href=\"https://kimetsu-no-yaiba.fandom.com/wiki/Hashira\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Hashira</em></a><em>.</em></p><p><strong><em>Hinatsuru</em></strong><em>&nbsp;is a supporting character of&nbsp;</em><a href=\"https://kimetsu-no-yaiba.fandom.com/wiki/Kimetsu_no_Yaiba_(Manga)\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba</em></a><em>. She is a&nbsp;</em><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kunoichi\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><em>kunoichi</em></a><em>&nbsp;and one of&nbsp;</em><a href=\"https://kimetsu-no-yaiba.fandom.com/wiki/Tengen_Uzui\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Tengen Uzui</em></a><em>'s wives.</em></p><p><strong><em>Makio</em></strong><em>&nbsp;is a supporting character of&nbsp;</em><a href=\"https://kimetsu-no-yaiba.fandom.com/wiki/Kimetsu_no_Yaiba_(Manga)\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba</em></a><em>. She is a&nbsp;</em><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kunoichi\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><em>kunoichi</em></a><em>&nbsp;and one of&nbsp;</em><a href=\"https://kimetsu-no-yaiba.fandom.com/wiki/Tengen_Uzui\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Tengen Uzui</em></a><em>'s wives.</em></p><p><strong><em>Suma</em></strong><em>&nbsp;is a supporting character of&nbsp;</em><a href=\"https://kimetsu-no-yaiba.fandom.com/wiki/Kimetsu_no_Yaiba_(Manga)\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba</em></a><em>. She is a&nbsp;</em><a href=\"https://en.wikip